Amalungu ePey de Gale (AMs) axhalabile 'ngokubonakala ngathi ngama-muppets'
Kukho inkxalabo yamalungu ePalamente athile acebisa ukuba igama lawo liguqulwe libe ziiMembers of Parliament (MWPs).
Iphulo lokutshintsha igama leNdlu ibe yiNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yasePeyi de Gale.
Amalungu ePalamente kwicala lezopolitiko ayoyika ukuba aya kuthotywa.
Ilungu leBhunga eliMele iLabour Party lathi iqela alimelayo lixhalabile kukuba eli gama "livakala njengeTwp nePwp".
Kubafundi abangengabo basePey de Gale: NgesiWelsh, twp ithetha isiyatha kwaye pwp ithetha isidenge.
Ilungu leBhunga eliMele iPlaid lathi iqela liphela "alithandanga" kwaye lanika ezinye iimfuno.
Ummeli we-Pei de Gale Conservative Party uthe iqela lakhe "likulungele ukwamkela izimvo ezahlukeneyo" malunga notshintsho lwegama, kodwa wagxininisa ukuba akukho mahluko mkhulu phakathi kwe-MWP (iNdlu yoWiso-mthetho) kunye neMuppet (iDoll).
Kungenxa yesi sizathu le nto i-Welsh  w isetyenziswa ngendlela efanayo ne- Yorkshire English  u.
IKomiti yePalamente, ngoku elungiselela iprojekthi yomthetho wokutshintsha igama, ithe: "Isigqibo sokugqibela malunga nokuba amalungu ePalamente abizwa njani siya kuthathwa ngamalungu ePalamente ngokwawo".
Umthetho woRhulumente wase-Gale ka-2017 wanika amalungu e-Gale State Council igunya lokutshintsha igama.
NgoJuni, iKomishoni yazisa iziphumo zophando olwenziwayo apho uninzi lwabantu lwaxhasa ukuba iPalamente ibizwe ngokuba yiPalamente yasePey de Gaulle.
Kwimeko yokuqeshwa kwamalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho (AM), iKomishoni inike ithuba elikhulu lokuba abizwe ngokuba yiNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yasePeyi de Gale okanye i-WMP, kodwa ukhetho lwe-MWP lwalusekelwa kakhulu kwiingxoxo zoluntu.
Amalungu eBhunga abonakala ngathi aza kwenza ezinye izigqibo, kodwa kunzima ukuvumelana noMlawuli oPhezulu, u-Elin Jones, olindeleke ukuba enze isindululo senguqu kwiiveki.
Umthetho wenguqu uquka ezinye iinguqu kwindlela esebenza ngayo iBhunga, kubandakanya imigaqo yokugxothwa kwamalungu eBhunga (AM) kunye neendlela zeekomiti.
Amalungu eNdlu aya kuvotelwa isigqibo sokuba aya kuba yintoni igama xa ethetha ngomthetho.
