Intlanzi enenyama yenzakalise umntwana oneminyaka eli-13 ubudala xa yayizingela i-lobster eCalifornia
Abasemagunyeni bathi intlanzi eyinyama yabulala yaza yamosha inkwenkwe eneminyaka eli-13 ubudala ngoMgqibelo xa yayisithi gqi kwi-lobster e-California ngomhla wokuvula wexesha lokuzingela i-lobster.
Ukuhlaselwa kwenzeka ngaphambi nje kwe-7 ekuseni kufutshane neBeacon Waterfront e-Encinitas.
UChad Hammel uxelele i-KSWB-TV eSan Diego ukuba wayeza kutshona kunye nabahlobo bakhe malunga nesiqingatha seyure ngoMgqibelo ekuseni xa weva inkwenkwe ikhwaza ecela uncedo kwaye iqela lafika lizama ukumkhupha emanzini.
