UHammel uqhubeka esithi: "Ndakhwaza ndithi wonke umntu makaphume emanzini: 'Khangela intlanzi elele emanzini!'"
Inkwenkwe yathunyelwa ngenqwelomoya kwisibhedlele sabantwana iRady Children's Hospital eSan Diego apho ikhoyo ngoku.
Iintlanzi ezifuywayo eziye zahlasela aziziwa.
Kwinkomfa noonondaba, uCaptain Larry Giles, uMsindisi woLwandle, wathi iintlanzi eziphila ngenyama zabonwa kwezi ndawo kwiiveki ezimbalwa ezidlulileyo, kodwa azibonwanga njengeentlanzi eziphila ngenyama eziyingozi.
