Abasemagunyeni bavala ukufikelela elunxwemeni ukusuka ePonto Beach eCasablad ukuya eSwami's e-Ecinitas iiyure ezingama-48 ngenxa yezizathu zophando kunye nokhuseleko.
UGiles uthi, kukho iintlobo ezingaphezu kwe-135 zeentlanzi eziphila kule ndawo, kodwa ezininzi zazo zibonwa njengezingenabungozi.
Izicwangciso zikaSainsbury zokungena kwimarike yobuhle yase-UK
ISainsbury isondela kwiiBoots, iSuperdrug kunye neDebenhams ngeendlela zayo zokuthengisa iimpahla zokuthambisa kunye nabaxhasi abaziingcali.
Njengenxalenye yenyathelo elikhulu lokuya kwimarike ye-UK ye-$2.8 yezigidigidi ye-cosmetics, eqhubekayo nokukhula ngelixa imveliso yefashoni kunye nemveliso yasekhaya iyaqhubeka nokuhla, iivenkile ezinkulu ezithengisa izinto zokuthambisa ziya kuqhuba uvavanyo kwiivenkile ezili-11 ezikwiphondo kwaye zifikelele kwezinye iivenkile kunyaka olandelayo xa zibonakalisile ukuba ziyasebenza.
Utyalomali kwiimveliso zobuhle lufana nokujonga indlela iimarike eziphambili ezisebenzisa ngayo indawo eshalofini ukufaka iiTV, iimakrofoni kunye nezixhobo zasekhaya.
USainsbury's uthe unokuphinda kabini umthamo weemveliso zokuthengisa ukuya kwiimveliso ezingama-3 000, kubandakanya iimveliso ezinkulu ezinje ngeRevlon, Essie, Tweezerman kunye noGqirha PawPaw okokuqala.
Iimpawu eziqhelekileyo ezifana neL'Oreal, Maybelline kunye neBurt's Bees ziya kuba nendawo eyaneleyo yokubeka iimveliso ezinkulu ezifanayo kwiivenkile ezinjengeeBhoots.
Iimarike eziphuhlisiweyo nazo ziqala ukuvelisa iivenkile zezinto zokuthambisa ukuze iimveliso ezininzi zilungele ukutya inyama; into efunwa ngabathengi abancinci.
Kwaye, umthengisi wevumba kwivenkile yevumba uza kujonga ukuba singayisebenzisa njani iivenkile ezimbini zeSainsburys, eyokuqala ivule eCroydon, kumazantsi eLondon, kwiveki ephelileyo kwaye eyesibini izakuvula eSelly Oak, eBirmingham, kamva kulo nyaka.
Ukuthenga kwi-Intanethi kukuguquka kokuthenga ukutya okuncinci kwiivenkile ezinkulu ezikufutshane, oko kuthetha ukuba iivenkile ezinkulu kufuneka zenze okungakumbi ukutsala abathengi.
UMike Coupe, u-CEO weSainsbury's, uthe ezi venkile ziya kwanda njengevenkile enkulu njengoko iivenkile ezinkulu zizama ukujongana nabahlaseli ababandakanya u-Aldi noLidl abanikezela ngeenkonzo ezininzi kwaye bangabandakanyi ukutya.
ISainsbury's ibeka iivenkile ezincinci zeArgos kwiivenkile zayo ezingaphezu kwekhulu kwaye yavula iivenkile ezibizwa ngokuba ziiHabitats njengoko yathenga igama levenkile ezimbini kwiminyaka emibini edlulileyo, oko kuthetha ukuba inyuse ukuthengisa ukutya kwayo kwaye yenze ingeniso ephezulu.
Uvavanyo lwevenkile enkulu yokuthengisa izinto zokuthambisa kunye namayeza lokuguqula amasebe alo lwaphela ngelize.
ISainsbury's yazama ukudibanisa ishishini neBoots ekuqaleni kweminyaka yoo-2000, kodwa ukudibana kwaphela ngokungavisisani ukuze babelane ngemali evela kwiivenkile zabo zeziyobisi kwiivenkile zayo ezinkulu.
Amanyathelo amatsha eza emva kokuba iSainsbury's ithengise iivenkile zayo ezingama-281 zezamayeza kuCelesio, umnini weLloyds Pharmacy, nge-£125 yezigidi kwiminyaka emithathu eyadlulayo.
ULloyds kuthiwa wabandakanyeka kule nkqubo, wongeza ezinye iintlobo zeoyile yomzimba ezibiza kakhulu kubandakanya iLa Roche-Posay kunye neVichy kwiivenkile ezine.
UPaul Mills-Hicks, oyintloko yentengiso eSainsbury's, uthi: "Sitshintshe indlela esibonakala ngayo nesivakalelwa ngayo kwivenkile yokuthengisa izinto ezintle ukuze siphucule indawo abathengi bethu abahlala kuyo.
Siye samema oogxa bethu abaqeqeshiweyo ukuba beze kuthi banike iingcebiso.
Iintlanga zethu zenzelwe ukuba zilungele zonke iimfuno kunye nomtsalane kunye nendawo efanelekileyo, oko kuthetha ukuba ngoku sihlala sifuna izixhobo zobuhle eziphikisana nendlela endala yokuthenga".
