Kodwa iCromwell Society yachaza isindululo sikaMnu. Crick "njengobudenge" kwaye "njengokuzama ukubhala imbali kwakhona".
UJohn Goldsmith, umlawuli weCromwell Society wathi: "Ayikho into enokuphepheka kule ngxoxo malunga nokususa imifanekiso eqingqiweyo ka-Oliver Cromwell ngaphandle kweIbhotwe laseWestminster.
