Ukubonakaliswa kukaCromwell nguSir William Hamo Thorneycroft kungumqondiso wenkulungwane ye-19 kwimbono kunye nenxalenye yembali yodongwe apho abaninzi bakholelwa ukuba isathandwa.
UGoldsmith uxelele iThe Sunday Telegraph: "UCromwell uthathwa njengento eninzi, mhlawumbi ngasekupheleni kwenkulungwane ye-19 kunangoku, njengento eyenza ukuba iPalamente ingabi nempembelelo ngaphandle ekulawuleni ubukhosi.
Nokuba oko kwakubonakaliswa njani, yinto ehlala ixutyushwa kwiindaba zembali.
Into eyinyani kukuba, ingxabano yexesha le-17th century yayibangelwa kukuphuhliswa kwamazwe ethu kwaye uCromwell ngumntu owaziwayo ukuba ubonakalisa icala elinye lale ngxabano.
