Izaqhwithi ezabangelwa yiNkanyamba uRosa zabangela imvula eninzi kummandla osemazantsi ntshona eUnited States
Ngokweemeko zemozulu, iSiphango uRosa siya sisiba buthathaka njengoko sihamba emanzini abandayo kunxweme olusemantla eMexico.
Noko ke, iSiphango Rosa siza kuzisa izantyalantyala zemvula kumantla eMexico nakumazantsi-ntshona eUnited States kwiintsuku ezizayo.
INkanyamba uRosa yayinezivunguvungu eziphezulu eziziikhilomitha ezili-136 ngeyure, ibe yayikwiCandelo 1 ngo-5:00 kusasa ngeCawa, ngexesha lasempuma, yaye yabonwa kumgama oziikhilomitha ezingama-620 kumzantsi-ntshona wePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
URosa kulindeleke ukuba aye emantla ngeCawa.
Ngelo xesha, isaqhwithi siqala ukuqina kwi-Pacific Ocean kwaye siya ngasentshona kunxweme lwaseNtshona lwe-US. Ngelixa iRosa isondela kwi-Baja California Peninsula ngoMvulo njengesaqhwithi esinyikima esiza kuqala ukufikelela kwimimoya esinyikima emantla nasemazantsi mpuma e-US.
URosa uza kuzisa imvula enokuba ziisentimitha ezingama-25 kwiindawo ezithile zaseMexico ngoMvulo.
Ngoku, imozulu yetropiki iya kudibana neqhwithi ezayo kwaye yenze imvula enkulu eninzi emazantsi ntshona kwiintsuku ezizayo.
Kulo mmandla, imvula encinane enokuba ziisentimitha eziyi-2,5 ukuya kweziyi-10 inokudala izikhukula, ukuwa kwamanzi, nokukhukuliseka komhlaba.
Ukubanda okuphezulu kweetropiki kuya kubangela imvula enokuhla ukusuka kwi-5 ukuya kwi-7 cm ngeyure kwangoko; ngakumbi kumazantsi eNevada naseArizona.
Ngexesha apho imvula ivela kwi-5 ukuya kwi-10 cm kulindeleke ukuba yehle kwiindawo ezisemzantsi, ikakhulu eArizona.
Izikhukula ezinokwenzeka ngokukhawuleza ziyenzeka apho zinokunciphisa khona ngenxa yemvula yeetropiki.
Kusenokungabi bubulumko ukuhamba entlango apho kunokuvela imvula yetropiki.
Imvula eninzi inokujika iintlambo zibe ziinqanawa ezinamandla yaye izantyalantyala zemvula zinokuvelisa iziphango ezinamandla ezinokuvelisa uthuli.
Iinkanyamba ziza kubangela imvula enkulu kwiindawo eziselunxwemeni lwaseMzantsi California.
Imvula inokufikelela kwisentimitha enye, nto leyo enokubangela ukuba umonakalo omncinane ugqithe uze wenze iindlela zigungqise.
Oku kuya kuba yimvula yokuqala kule ndawo ngexesha lehlobo.
Ezinye zeemvula ezitshisayo eziza kuqala ukufikelela eArizona ngeCawa ngeeyure eziphezulu nangeMvulo ekuseni, ngaphambi kokuba kubekho imvula enkulu ngeCawa nangeLwesibini ekuseni.
Imvula enzima iya kufikelela kwiindawo ezine ezikwikona ngoLwesibini nangoLwesithathu.
Ngo-Okthobha kunokubakho utshintsho olukhulu lobushushu eMelika njengoko iArctic iya isiba kubanda, kodwa iitropiki ziyaqhubeka zishushu.
Ngamanye amaxesha oku kubangela utshintsho olukhulu lobushushu kunye nomgama omncinci.
Kukho umzekelo ophawulekayo womahluko obukhulu wobushushu phakathi kwe-US ngeCawa.
Kukho umahluko wobushushu obuphantse bube ngama-20 degrees Celsius phakathi kweKansas City, eMissouri naseOmaha, eNebraska naphakathi kweSt. Louis neDes Moines, eIowa.
Kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo, ubushushu basehlotyeni buya kuzama ukubuyela phezulu.
Amaqondo obushushu amaninzi kwi-US Central nase-East kulindeleke ukuba afike kwi-26 degrees Celsius ukusuka eMzantsi Merika ukuya eMantla mpuma ngo-Okthobha.
Isixeko saseNew York City sinokufikelela kuma-26 degrees Celsius ngoLwesibini, phantse ama-10 degrees Celsius ngaphezulu komndilili.
Iinkqubo zethu zexesha elide zibonisa ukuba kukho ithuba eliphezulu lokuba amaqondo obushushu angaphezulu komyinge afike kwiindawo ezikuMntla Merika ukuya kuthi ga kwisiqingatha sokuqala sika-Okthobha.
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele ityala likaBrett Kavanaugh
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele ubungqina obumangalisayo obunikwe nguMongameli weNkundla ePhakamileyo uBrett Kavanaugh kunye nommangaleli wakhe wokunyanzelwa ngokwesondo ngo-1980, uChristine Blasey Ford, kumajelo eendaba amathandathu.
Okwangoku, ukungavisisani kwezopolitiko kuqhubeke, kunye nabapapashi beendaba beTV abaphazamisa ingxoxo yabo yaseburhulumenteni ngoLwesihlanu ngomzuzu wokugqibela: Isivumelwano esenziwe nguSenator waseArizona uJeff Flake sokuba i-FBI iphando ngolwaphulo-mthetho olwenziwa kuye kwiveki.
UFord uxelele iKomiti ye-Senate yokuPhepha ukuThintela ukuba uqinisekile nge-100% ukuba uKavanaugh wamtyhola esele utywala kwaye wazama ukumkhulula kwitheko lesikolo esiphakamileyo.
UKavanaugh, onikela ubungqina obubonisa imibala, wathi uqinisekile nge-100% ukuba oku akwenzekanga.
Kubonakala ngathi abantu abangaphezu kwe-20.4 yezigidi bafumana ingxelo kaNielsen ngoLwesihlanu.
Inkampani ibibala inani labantu ababukela i-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kunye ne-MSNBC.
Amanani awafumanekanga kwangoko avela kwamanye amajelo eendaba abonisa ubungqina obubandakanya i-PBS, i-C-SPAN kunye ne-Fox Business Network.
Kwaye uNielsen uhlala eneengxaki zokubalwa kwabantu ababukela iintetho kwiofisi.
Ukucacisa, bangabantu abafana ne-Award of Merit okanye i-Academy Awards.
UNielsen uthi: I-Fox News Channel, eneendwendwe ezixhasa kakhulu ukhetho luka-Kavanaugh, ikhokela ezinye iinkqubo ngokubukela okuqhelekileyo kwezigidi ezi-5.69 ngexesha lokutsalwa kwetyala ngosuku lonke.
I-ABC yaba kwindawo yokuqala ngamanani ayi-3.26 ezigidi ezibonwayo.
U-Nelsen uthi: I-CBS ibukele izigidi ezi-3.1, i-NBC ibukele izigidi ezi-2.4, i-MSNBC ibukele izigidi ezi-2.89 kwaye i-CNN ibukele izigidi ezi-2.52.
Kuninzi okunomdla emva kwetyala lakhe.
UFlake wayejonge iziganeko ezenzeka ngoLwesihlanu.
Emva kokuba i-Républicain Bureau yenze isibhengezo sokumxhasa uKavanaugh, wafota nge-CNN kunye ne-CBS kusasa ngoLwesihlanu ekhwankqiswa ngabaqhankqalazi njengoko wayezama ukungena kwilifti eya kwityala leKomiti yezoBulungisa.
Wajonga phantsi imizuzu emininzi njengoko wayegxekwa, kwaye oko kwaboniswa kwi-CNN.
"Ndimi phambi kwenu", watsho omnye umfazi.
"Ngaba ucinga ukuba uthetha inyaniso kubantu belizwe lonke?
Wathi, "Unamandla amaninzi xa uninzi lwabafazi lungenamandla"".
UFlake wathi iofisi yakhe yayingazi ukuba yintoni eyenzekayo kwaye wathi ngaphambi kokuba i-elevator ivale, wathetha kakhulu kwi-audience yekomiti.
Iitshaneli zeTV kunye nezitishi zeendaba zazisandula ukuqala ukubonakala emva kweeyure ezimbalwa, xa iKomiti yeZibheno yavota ukuhambisa uKavanaugh ukuya kwinqanaba elilandelayo ukuze afike kwiSenate ukuze akhethe.
Kodwa uFlake wathi uza kwenza njalo kuphela ukuba uyazi ukuba i-FBI ifuna ukuvavanya izityholo ezichasene nomntu otyunjwe kwiveki ezayo, nto leyo ebicelwa ngamaDemocrat ambalwa.
UFlake waqondwa njengelinye lamaqela aphumeleleyo kwingxoxo nomhlobo wakhe, uMongameli weDemocratic uChris Coons.
Emva kokuxoxa noCoons namanye amalungu eNdlu yeeNgwevu kamva, uFlake wenza isigqibo.
Ukhetho lukaFlake lwalunamandla, kuba kwakubonakala ngathi amaRephabliki ayengenakuvota ukuqinisekisa ukuba uKavanaugh akahlolwa.
UMongameli Trump uvule uphando lwe-FBI malunga nezityholo ezenziwa nguKavanaugh.
