Iqela eliphakanyisiweyo iLivingston libetha iRangers, yaba kukuphulukana kwesibini kukaSteven Gerrard kwimidlalo eli-18 njengomphathi weIbrox.
Inqaku likaDolly Menga labonisa umahluko njengoko iqela likaGary Holt lalihamba laya kwindawo yesibini lifumana iHibernian.
Iqela likaGerrard aliphumelelanga kwiqela elalityelele iChampionship kulo nyaka kwaye liza kudibana neqela eliphambili kwiChampionship, iHearts, elandela ngamanqaku asibhozo, ngeCawa.
Ngaphambi koko, iRangers izakwamkela iRapid Vienna kumdlalo we-Europa League ngoLwesine.
Okwangoku, iLivingston, iye yandisa imbali yayo yokungoyiswa kwiligi ukuya kuthi ga kwimidlalo emithandathu, apho umqeqeshi wayo ophezulu uHolt ebekulindeleke ukuba oyiswe ukusukela oko wathatha indawo kaKenny Miler kwinyanga ephelileyo.
