UScott Robinson wakwazi ukugqitha kumagosa okhuselo kodwa ibhola yadlula ecaleni komgcini kwaye uAlan Lithgow wakwazi ukubetha ibhola yakhe ngaphandle emva kokutyibilika ukuze adibane nebhola eyayibetha intloko kaCraig Halkett.
Ababuki zindwendwe babevuyiswa kukuvumela iRangers idlale phambi kwabo, besazi ukuba banokubuza iindwendwe zabo kwiibhola zokudlala.
Ngaloo ndlela kwafunyanwa umqobo obalulekileyo.
I-Rangers ilahlekelwe yibhola yokuqala kwaye u-Livingston uvule umnxeba, u-Declan Gallagher no-Robinson badibana ukuze bafumane inqaku lika-Menga, owabamba umzimba wakhe embindini wenethiwekhi.
Kule nqanaba, iRangers yayinebholo ekhethekileyo kodwa yafumana udonga lwangasemva lweqela elalityeleleyo lungakhange luphulwe kwaye umgcini, uLiam Kelly, owayengakhange akhuphe ibhola enkulu,
Umdlalo waqhubeka kwisiqingatha sesibini nangona uAlfredo Morelos wabetha ibhola yabuya yafunyanwa nguKelly.
Ibhola kaScott Pittman yabekwa phantsi ziinyawo zikaRangers uAllan McGregor, kwaye uLithgow waphakama emva kwebhola elandelayo kaLivingston.
Iimbumbulu zokuqala zokhuseleko zaqhubeka zifika kwi-website ye-Livingston kodwa zaqhubeka zikhuselekile ukuba zingafikeleli kwicala lokhuseleko, ngelixa kwakuthethwa ukuba kukho izohlwayo ezibini, emva kokuba uHalkett enze impazamo kuGlenn Middleton owayengumdlali obekiweyo kunye nebhola yesandla, zombini ezo zinto azizange zenziwe.
