INkanyamba uRose ixhalabisa iPhoenix, eLas Vegas, eSalt Lake City ngenxa yezikhukula ezikhawulezayo (Iindawo ezichaphazelekayo yembalela zinokuzuza)
Kunqabile ukuba iinkanyamba zihlasele iArizona, kodwa zinokwenzeka ekuqaleni kweveki ezayo xa amandla esisele esiphepho uRosa efikelela kwintlango ekumzantsi-ntshona, ebangela izikhukula.
I-National Weather Service ilumkise ngezikhukula ezinamandla ngoMvulo nangoLwesibini ukusuka entshona Arizona ukuya emazantsi nasempuma Nevada, ngasempuma yeCalifornia naseUtah, kubandakanya iPhoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas neSalt Lake City.
URosa kulindeleke ukuba athathe indlela ethe ngqo eya ePhoenix ngoLwesibini, aze afike kwiiyure ezinemvula ngoMvulo.
I-National Weather Service yasePhoenix ithi "iinkanyamba ezilishumi ezibangelwa yimvula ezinamandla okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya enamandla okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu okanye iinkanyamba ezibangele ukuba kubekho imimoya emikhulu kwiPhenix ukususela ngowe-1950!"
Inkanyamba uKatrina (1967) yayiyeyona inkanyamba yavela kumgama oziikhilomitha ezingama-64 ukusuka kumda we-AZ".
I-National Hurricane Center iye yaqulunqa imodeli yemvula enokuba ziisentimitha ezi-5 ukuya kwezi-10 okanye ezimalunga nezi-15 eMogollon Rim, eArizona.
Ezinye iindawo ezisemzantsi-ntshona, eziquka indawo ephakathi kweeRockies kunye neGreat Basin, zinokufumana imvula enamanzi ukusuka kwi-2 ukuya kwi-5 cm, mhlawumbi ukuya kuthi ga kwi-10 cm.
Kwabo bangenalo ixhala lokutshatyalaliswa zizikhukula, imvula kaRosa inokuba yintsikelelo emva kokuba ummandla uchaphazelwe yimbalela.
Nangona imvula inzima kakhulu, ezinye zezi mvula zinokuzisa izibonelelo kwi-hemisphere esemazantsi-ntshona kwindawo eyomileyo.
I-Wetter.com inikela ingxelo yokuba ngokwe-National Center for Drought Monitoring, ngaphezulu kwe-40% yaseArizona ubuncinci inembalela enkulu, eyona ndawo iphezulu.
Okokuqala, indlela kaRosa ikhokelela kumhlaba okwicala elingaselunxwemeni lwaseBaja California, eMexico.
URosa, useneziphango zomoya ngeCawa, unomoya omkhulu oziikhilomitha ezili-136 ngeyure, kwaye ukwiikhilomitha ezingama-620 kumzantsi wePunta Eugenia, eMexico usiya emantla ngeekhilomitha ezingama-20 ngeyure.
Umoya uhlangana namanzi abandayo olwandle lwePasifiki kwaye unciphisa isantya.
Ngoko ke, kulindeleke ukuba ifike eMexico njengomoya onamandla asezantsi embindini welizwe emva kwemini okanye ngokuhlwa ngoMvulo.
Imvula eninzi inokugalela kwiindawo ezithile zaseMexico, nto leyo enokubangela izikhukula ezinokuba yingozi.
IWetter.com ithi: "Imvula epheleleyo inokubangela ukuba kubekho imvula engange-7 ukuya kwi-15 cm ukusuka eBaja California ukuya kutsho kumntla-mpuma weSonora, apho imvula engange-25 cm inokwenzeka".
URosa uza kuthi emva koko aqhubeke nokuya emantla eMexico njengesaqhwithi ngaphambi kokufikelela kumda waseArizona ngentsasa yangoLwesibini, ngelixa isaqhwithi esishushu siza kuqhubela phambili siwela eArizona siye emazantsi eUtah ngentsasa yangoLwesibini.
I-National Hurricane Center ithi: "Eyona ngxaki inkulu kulindelwe ukuba yenzeke kuRosa okanye kwizaqhwithi ezibangelwa nguye yimvula enkulu eBaja California, kumntla ntshona weSonora nakwiNtlango yaseMzantsi Ntshona".
Le mvula kulindeleke ukuba ibangele izikhukula ezinobungozi, eziya kubangela ukuba abantu babulawe ziinkunkuma, zize zikhokelele entlango, zize zibangele ukuba iindawo ezintabeni zibe nodaka.
