Amakhulu abantu ababulewe yinyikima, itsunami ehlasela iIndonesia, apho inani labantu abaswelekileyo liqhubeka lisanda
NgoMgqibelo, abasemagunyeni bathi ubuncinane abantu abangama-384 babulawa, uninzi lwabo lusweleka ngenxa yezikhukula ezithe zathwaxa unxweme, xa inyikima enkulu kunye netsunami zatshabalalisa isiqithi saseIndonesia iSulawesi.
NgolwesiHlanu, abantu abangaphezu kwamakhulu babuthelene kwindawo yokuzonwabisa elunxwemeni kwisixeko sasePalu xa imimoya engangeemitha ezili-18 yahlasela unxweme ngokuhlwa, yabulala abantu abaninzi yaza yonakalisa yonke into eyayihamba endleleni.
Iitsunami zalandela inyikima enkulu enobungakanani obuyi-7.5.
USutopo Purwo Nugroho, isithethi se-BNPB, i-Indonesian National Disaster Management Agency, wathi kwingxoxo eJakarta: "Njengoko imeko ye-tsunami yayinyuka izolo, abantu babesenza imisebenzi yabo kunxweme kwaye abazange babaleke ngokukhawuleza kwaye bafa".
"Itsunami ayizange ize ililize, yafika yahamba neemoto, imithi, amanzi, yahamba nayo yonke into eyayikho emhlabeni", utshilo uNugroho, esithi itsunami yafika elwandle ngesantya seekhilomitha ezingama-800 ngeyure (i-497 miles ngeyure) ngaphambi kokuba ibethe unxweme.
Uthi abanye abantu baye banyuka imithi ukuze basinde kutsunami.
Abantu abamalunga ne-16,700 basuswa kuloo ndawo baza basiwa kwiinkampu eziyi-24 ePalu.
Iifoto zomoya ezikhutshwe yi-CIS zibonisa izakhiwo ezininzi nevenkile ezonakeleyo, iibhulorho ezonakeleyo kunye nezikhukula.
NgoMgqibelo, inyikima encinane elandelayo enkulu yaqhubeka itshisa izixeko eziselunxwemeni.
Iinyikima ezahlukahlukeneyo zazivala kwiindawo ezinabantu abamalunga nezigidi eziyi-2,4.
I-Indonesian Bureau of Project and Analysis Technology (BPPT) ithe inyikima yangoLwesihlanu yayinamandla phantse aphindwe ka-200 kunebhombu yeathom eyaphoswa eHiroshima ngexesha leMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Le ngxelo ithi, ngenxa yendlela esi sixeko esiyiyo, indawo esikuyo enxweme inokubangela iitsunami.
UNugroho uchaze umonakalo "njengobunzulu" kwaye wathi amawaka ezindlu, iikliniki, iivenkile kunye neehotele zonakele.
Izidumbu zafunyanwa phakathi kwezindlu ezidilikileyo, zongeza kubantu abangama-540 abenzakeleyo kunye nabanye abangama-29 abangekhoyo.
UNugroho uthe abantu ababuleweyo nomonakalo unokuba mkhulu kunxweme olungaphezulu kweekhilomitha ezingama-300 (iimayile ezingama-190) kumantla ePalu, kwindawo ebizwa ngokuba yiDonggala, kufutshane nendawo yenyikima.
UGugroho uthi ukufikelela nokudluliselwa kweenkcukacha "kwakungathintelwa kakhulu apho kwakungekho nkcazelo inokuhamba" ukusuka eDonggala.
Ngokutsho kweRed Cross, abantu abangama-300 000 bahlala kule ngingqi", kwaye yongeza ukuba abasebenzi bayo kunye namavolontiya baya kuya kwiindawo ezichaphazelekayo.
Uthi: "Kudala kuyingozi, kodwa kusenokuba kubi nangakumbi".
NgoMgqibelo, iziko lachaza ukuba lifumene ugxekwa olukhulu ngenxa yokungabikho kwengxelo yesaziso se-tsunami ePalu, kodwa abasemagunyeni bathi amaza afika ngexesha lokulumkisa.
Iifoto ezenziwe ngabantu abangengobakhenkethi ezabelwana ngazo kwi-intanethi zibonisa indoda ehleli phezulu kwisakhiwo apho iqubha khona ikhwaza isilumkisa abantu ukuba itsunami iza kufikela abantu abasesitratweni esingezantsi kwayo.
Kwimizuzu embalwa amanzi agqabhuka anqumla unxweme, ehamba nezakhiwo neemoto.
