UMongameli waseMexico uAMLO ufunge ukuba akasayi kusebenzisa umkhosi wokulwa nabantu basekuhlaleni
Umongameli onyulwe waseMexico uAndres Manuel Lopez Obrador ufunge ukuba akasayi kuze asebenzise umkhosi wokulwa nabantu abaqhelekileyo njengoko ilizwe lisondela kumhla wama-50 wokuzalwa kobhokoxo lwabafundi.
NgoMgqibelo, uLopez Obrador kwiTlatelolco Plaza waqinisekisa ukuba "akayi kuze asebenzise umkhosi ukuthulisa abantu baseMexico".
Umkhosi wadubula abantu ababethe cwaka kwibhotwe ngo-Oktobha 2, 1968, wabulala abantu abangama-300 ngexesha lokuqhambuka kwemfazwe yabafundi abachasene norhulumente kwilizwekazi laseMntla Melika.
ULopez Obrador uqinisekisile ukuba ulutsha lwaseMexico luza kuncedwa ngemali yabafundi kwaye iiyunivesithi zikawonkewonke ziya kuvulwa.
Uthi ukungaqeshwa nokungafumani thuba lokufunda kwenza ulutsha lube ngamaxhoba olwaphulo-mthetho.
I-US kufuneka iphindwe kabini imali ebinikelwa kubugcisa bobugcisa
Ngelixa i-China isenza imisebenzi emininzi ye-AI, i-US kufuneka iphindwe kabini inkcitho yayo kuphando lwe-AI, utshilo usomashishini we-AI uKai-Fu Lee, osebenzele uGoogle, iMicrosoft kunye neApple.
Olu luvo luza emva kokuba amacandelo amaninzi karhulumente wase-US enze ingxelo malunga nobuchule bokuyila; nangona i-US ngokubanzi ingenayo imigaqo-nkqubo eyaziwayo malunga nobuchule bokuyila.
Okwangoku, i-China isungule inkqubo yayo kunyaka ophelileyo: ijolise ekubeni ngowokuqala ukuvelisa izinto ezintsha kubugcisa bokuzenzela ngo-2030.
"Ukuphinda kabini imali efunyenwe kuphando lobukrelekrele bokuzenzela kuya kuba sisiqalo esihle, kuba amanye amazwe asesemva kakhulu eMelika kwaye sifuna ukufikelela kubuchule obuphezulu be-AI", utshilo uLee.
Ukuphinda kabini imali yokuxhasa ngemali kunokuphinda kabini amathuba okufikelela kwiinkampani ezinkulu zaseMelika, utshilo uLee kwi-CNBC kule veki.
U-Lee, umbhali wencwadi ethi "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley kunye neNew World Order" yapapashwa kule nyanga ngu-Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, onguMlawuli oyiNtloko we-Sinovation Ventures, inkampani etyale imali kwiinkampani eziphambili zobukrelekrele bokuzenzela zase China, u-Face ++.
Ngeminyaka yoo 1980 kwiYunivesithi yaseCarnegie Mellon, wenza inkqubo yokusebenzisa ubuchule bokuzenzela obugqwesileyo kunomdlali weqonga waseMelika uOthello, kamva waba yi-CEO yeMicrosoft Research kwaye waba yintloko yeGoogle e China.
U-Lee wavuma ukhuphiswano lobugcisa bakarhulumente wase-US olufana ne-Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency's Robotics Challenge kwaye wabuzwa ukuba uza kubanjwa nini ukhuphiswano olulandelayo ukunceda ekuboneni iingcali zexesha elizayo.
ULee uthi abaphandi baseMerika badla ngokuzama ukufumana inkxaso-mali karhulumente.
"I-China ayithethi nje ngootitshala ababalaseleyo, kodwa ithetha ngeenkampani", utshilo uLee.
I-Facebook, iGoogle kunye nezinye iinkampani zetekhnoloji ziye zaqesha iingcali eziphambili zeyunivesithi ukuba zisebenze kwiiprojekthi zobuchule bokuzenzela kule minyaka imbalwa idlulileyo.
U-Lee wathi utshintsho kumgaqo-nkqubo wokufudukela kwelinye ilizwe lunokunceda i-US ukuba ibe namandla ngakumbi kubuchule.
"Ndicinga ukuba ilungelo lokuhlala ngokusisigxina eMelika, elibizwa ngokuba yi green card, kufuneka linikwe ngokukhawuleza kwabo baneziqu ze-master kwi-biology", utshilo.
Ibhunga likarhulumente wase China lakhupha iSicwangciso soPhuhliso lwe-AI kwizigaba ezilandelayo ngoJulayi 2017.
U-Lee uthi i-NGO yase-China ixhasa abantu kwizikolo ngendlela efanayo ne-NGO kunye neminye imibutho karhulumente exhasa abaphandi base-US, kodwa imisebenzi yezemfundo isezantsi e-China.
Ekuqaleni konyaka, iSebe lezoKhuselo lase-US laseka i-Artificial Intelligence Joint Center, nto leyo ethetha ukuba ukusebenzisana phakathi kweshishini kunye nezikolo kuya kuphuculwa kwaye uMongameli wase-US wabhengeza ukusekwa kweKomiti ekhethekileyo yokujonga ubuchule bokuzenzela.
Kwaye kule nyanga i-DARPA ibhengeze ukuba izakutyala imali eyi-$2 billion kwiprojekthi yayo ebizwa ngokuba yi-AI Next.
Ngokuphathelele iNSF, ngoku ityala imali engaphezulu kwe-$100 yezigidi ngonyaka kuphando lobukrelekrele bokuzenzela.
Okwangoku, abenzi bomthetho baseMelika bafuna iKomishoni yeSizwe yoKhuseleko lweNgqondo emva kweenyanga ezininzi bengakhange benze nto.
