Ukusuka kwiziphumo zovavanyo zamva nje kulo nyaka, sinokubona ukuba iilwimi ziphezulu kwiitshathi apho ziye zaphumelela kakhulu kwizikolo ezizimeleyo.
I-68 pesenti yabafundi abafunda ulwimi lwasemzini bafumana amanqaku aphezulu kunalawo afunyenwe ngabafundi abafunda kwelinye ilizwe.
Iinkcukacha eziqokelelwe yiSCIS kwizikolo eziyi-74 ezibandakanyekayo zibonisa ukuba abafundi abangama-72 ekhulwini bafumana amanqaku aphezulu kwisiMandarin, ngoxa abangama-72 ekhulwini befumana amanqaku aphezulu kwisiJamani, ama-69 ekhulwini befumana amanqaku aphezulu kwisiFrentshi nama-63 ekhulwini befumana amanqaku aphezulu kwisiSpanish.
Ibonisa ukuba izikolo ezizimeleyo eScotland zixhasa iilwimi zangaphandle njengolwazi olubalulekileyo abantwana nolutsha abaya kulufuna kwixesha elizayo.
Ngoku iilwimi, njengesifundo esifanelekileyo, zixhaswa zezinye izifundo ze-STEM (inzululwazi, itekhnoloji, ubunjineli kunye nezibalo) kwizifundo ezikhethekileyo okanye kwezinye iindawo.
Uphando olwenziwe yi-UK Commission on Employment and Skills ngo-2014 lwafumanisa ukuba iipesenti ezili-17 zezizathu zokuba abaqeshi babe nobunzima bokufumana abantu abafanelekileyo kwizikhundla ezisemthethweni zibangelwa kukungazi kakuhle iilwimi.
Ngoko ke, ulwazi lweelwimi luya kuba yimfuneko ukulungiselela ulutsha kumsebenzi walo wexesha elizayo.
Nangona imisebenzi emininzi ifuna ulwimi, olu lwazi lubalulekile kwihlabathi eliye laba sisixeko.
Nokuba yeyiphi na imisebenzi, xa ufunda ulwimi lwesibini, unethuba elihle lokufumana ulwazi lobomi bonke.
Ukukwazi ukunxibelelana ngqo nabanye abantu kumazwe angaphandle kwenza ukuba umntu akwazi ukufumana ulwazi oluthe kratya phambi kwabanye abantu abakhuphisana nabo kwimarike.
Ngokophando olwenziwe ngu-YouGov kubantu abadala abangaphezu kwama-4,000 base-UK ngo-2013, ama-75 ekhulwini abakwazi ukuthetha ulwimi lwasemzini kakuhle ngokwaneleyo ukuba banokuncokola, ngelixa isiFrentshi lulwimi kuphela oluthethwa ngabantu abangaphezu kweshumi, ama-15 ekhulwini.
Yiyo loo nto ukutyala imali ekufundiseni iilwimi kubalulekile kubantwana bale mihla.
Ukuba neelwimi ezininzi, ngakumbi kumazwe asakhasayo, kunika abantwana amathuba amaninzi okufumana imisebenzi enentsingiselo.
Izikolo zaseScotland ziyahluka ngokolwimi.
Izikolo ezininzi ziya kugxininisa kwiilwimi zangoku, ngelixa ezinye zifundisa iilwimi eziza kuthathwa njengezibalulekileyo eNgilane ngo-2020, ezinje ngesiMandarin okanye isiJapan.
Enoba yintoni umntwana wakho ayithandayo, kusoloko kukho iilwimi ezikhethwayo kwizikolo zabucala, apho ootitshala beelwimi abaziingcali.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo eScotland zizimisele ukufundisa ngendlela yokulungiselela abantwana nokubabonelela ngolwazi olufunekayo ukuze baphumelele, nokuba kwenzeka ntoni na.
Ayikwazi kukhanyela ukuba namhlanje, kurhwebo lwamazwe ngamazwe, iilwimi zihlala zibalulekile kwikamva lelizwe, kwaye ke kufuneka zibonakaliswe kwimfundo.
Ewe, iilwimi zanamhlanje kufuneka zithathwe njenge"zixhobo zolwazi ezinika ulwazi kwihlabathi liphela".
Izikolo ezizimeleyo ziyaqhubeka nokubonelela ngezi ndlela, iindlela ezahlukeneyo ezingafikelelekiyo kulutsha lwaseScotland.
