Iphulo elimiselweyo liza kubanjelwa eWesbanco Arena eWheeling, kwaye liphulo elinokuzisa abaphembeleli abavela "eOhio nasePennsylvania kwaye liza kubhengezwa kwiphephandaba lasePittsburgh", ngokutsho kweWest Virginia Metro News.
