INorth Korea ithi 'akukho ndlela' yokulahla izixhobo zayo zenyukliya kwilizwe elinye ngaphandle kwethemba
NgoMgqibelo, umphathiswa wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea uxelele iZizwe eziManyeneyo ukuba ukusetyenziswa kweziqhinelo kuya kukhulisa ukungathembani ne-US kwaye akukho ndlela yokuba ilizwe lilahle inkqubo yalo yenyukliya phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo.
U-Ri Yong Ho uxelele amagosa aseburhulumenteni kwiNdibano yoNyaka ukuba "kwathatyathwa amanyathelo afanelekileyo" kunyaka ophelileyo, njengokumisa uvavanyo lwenyukliya, ukutshabalalisa indawo yovavanyo lwenyukliya kunye nokuqinisekisa ukuba akukho kuphinda kwenziwe i-nuclear blasts kunye netekhnoloji yenyukliya.
"Nangona kunjalo, asiboni mpendulo ifanelekileyo evela e-US", utshilo.
"Akukho themba lokuba iMelika inokufumana ukuthembana kukhuseleko lwamazwe ethu kwaye ukuba kunjalo akukho ndlela yokuba thina njengelizwe elinye sinokuyeka ukwenza izixhobo zenyukliya kuqala".
Ngelixa uRi ephinda iingxelo eziqhelekileyo zaseMantla Korea malunga nokuzimisela kukaWashington ukuba "kwizigaba" zokurhoxisa imveliso yenyukliya apho iNyakatho Korea inokulawula umvuzo njengoko isenza inyathelo, amazwi akhe abonakala enentsingiselo nangona engakhange ayiphikise into yokuba urhulumente wasePyongyang angarhoxa kwimveliso yenyukliya njengoko wenzayo ngaphambili.
URi uthathe inxaxheba kwintetho kaMongameli uKim Jong Un noDonald Trump kwintlanganiso yokuqala yomongameli wase-US kunye nomongameli wase-North Korea eSingapore ngoJuni 12, apho uKim wayezithembile ukuba usebenza "ukuyeka ukwenza i-nuclear kwiPeninsula yaseKorea" ngelixa uTrump wayeqinisekisa ukhuseleko lwase-North Korea.
INorth Korea yayifuna ukuphela kweMfazwe yaseKorea yowe-1950-53, kodwa iUnited States yathi iPyongyang kufuneka iqale iyeke ukwenza izixhobo zayo zenyukliya.
IWashington iye yala ukunciphisa izigwebo ezinzima zamazwe ngamazwe ezibekwe kwiNyakatho Korea.
Ithi: "I-US iyaqhubeka nokugxininisa ukuba 'siqala ngokuyeka ukwenza izixhobo zenyukliya' kwaye inyuse uxinzelelo kunye nezithintelo ukuze ifikelele kwinjongo yabo ngamandla, nangona ingavumi 'ukuvakalisa ukuphela kwemfazwe.'"
"Ingcamango yokuba izohlwayo zisenokusenza siwele ezinyaweni zethu iphupha nje elingenakwenzeka kuluntu olungafuniyo ukusibona.
Kodwa ingxaki kukuba, ukuqhubeka kwezihlwayo kusenza sithembe ngakumbi".
URi akazange enze nazintetho malunga neenkqubo zendibano yesibini kaKim noTrump, apho umongameli wase-US wayethetha ngayo kwi-UN ekuqaleni kwale veki.
Endaweni yoko, umphathiswa ukhankanye iintlanganiso ezintathu phakathi kukaKim noMongameli waseMzantsi Korea, uMon Jae-in, kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo kwaye wathi: "Ukuba ilizwe elibhekise kulo mba wokupheliswa kweentolo zenyukliya yayinguMzantsi Korea hayi iMelika, ukuvalwa kweentolo zenyukliya zePeninsula yaseKorea ngekhe kwavalwa".
Kwaye, ithoni kaRi yayahluke kakhulu kunyaka ophelileyo, xa wayethetha kwiNdibano yeZizwe eziManyeneyo ukuba ukuzama ukuhlasela iMelika ngeerokethi zaseKorea kunokwenzeka emva kokuba "uMongameli ongenamdla" uTrump ebize uKim "njengendoda yebhombu" enesicwangciso sokuzibulala.
Kwingqungquthela yeZizwe eziManyeneyo kulo nyaka, uTrump, owathi kunyaka ophelileyo wasongela "ukutshabalalisa ngokupheleleyo" iNyakatho Korea, wancoma uKim ngokuzimisela kwakhe ukuthatha inyathelo lokurhoxisa imveliso yakhe, kodwa wathi kuninzi ekufuneka kwenziwe kwaye izigwebo ziyaqhubeka de iNyakatho Korea iyeke ukwenza imveliso yayo.
NgoLwesithathu, uTrump wathi akanalo ixesha lokwenza oku, esithi "Ukuba kuthatha iminyaka emibini, emithathu okanye iinyanga ezintathu; akunamsebenzi".
I-China ne-Russia baxambulisana ne-UN Security Council ukuba ihlawule urhulumente wase-Pyongyang ngesenzo sakhe.
Nangona kunjalo, uNobhala welizwe laseMelika uMike Pompeo uxelele iBhunga loKhuseleko ngoLwesine: "Ukomeleza izigwebo zeBhunga loKhuseleko kufuneka kuqhubeke ngokuqinileyo kwaye kungapheli mandla de kuboniswe ukuba i-nuclear isuswe ngokupheleleyo, ngokukhawuleza kwaye ihlolwe".
I-UNSC iye yavota ngokungagungqiyo ukwandisa imiqathango kwiNyakatho Korea ukusukela ngo-2006 ukuthintela ukuxhasa urhulumente wasePyongyang kwiinkqubo zayo zenyukliya kunye nezikrweqe.
UPompeo wadibana noRi kwintlanganiso eyingqayizivele ye-UN General Assembly kwaye kamva wathi uza kuphinda atyelele iPyongyang kwinyanga ezayo ukulungiselela intlanganiso yesibini.
UPompeo uye watyelela iNyakatho Korea kathathu kulo nyaka, kodwa utyelelo lwakhe lwamva nje aluzange luphumelele.
Ushiye iPyongyang ngoJulayi esithi kukho inyathelo elithathileyo, iiyure ezimbalwa kamva iNorth Korea yaphikisa oko yathi "iimfuno zifana neqela lamaphekula".
I-North Korea ithembise kwintlanganiso yayo no-Moon ukuba izakuqhekeza indawo yayo yokuvelisa i-missile kunye ne-nuclear facilities kule nyanga ukuba i-US "ithatha amanyathelo afanayo".
Uthe uKim umxelele ukuba "amanyathelo afanayo" afuna ukuba athathwe kukuqinisekisa ukhuseleko phantsi kwesivumelwano sikaTrump eSingapore kwaye uyaqhubeka nokulungisa ubudlelwane noWashington.
