'Ekugqibeleni, enye intombazana yeza kum yathi, 'Kutheni usandithetha nje, ekubeni ndikwunyaka wam wokugqibela ekholejini?'
Uthi akukho mntu wakha wamxelela ngokubaluleka kokulala, nto leyo eyandimangalisile,' utshilo kwiThe Telegraph.
Isifundo, esaqala ukuboniswa, sichaza abafundi ngeendlela zokulala ezincedayo ekuziphatheni kakuhle kwabafundi kunye nabadlali, kunye nokuphucula impilo ngokubanzi.
UPaul Barreira, unjingalwazi wempilo yengqondo kwiSebe lezeMpilo kwiYunivesithi yaseHarvard kunye nomlawuli ophezulu weenkonzo zempilo, wathi iyunivesithi yagqiba kwelokuba ifake isifundo emva kokuba abafundi belele iveki yonke.
Isifundo seyure sinemisebenzi eyahlukeneyo yonxibelelwano.
Kwelinye icala kukho umfanekiso wegumbi lokuhlala, apho abafundi bacofa iikomityi zekofu, amakhethini, izihlangu zokuzilolonga kunye neencwadi kwaye baxelelwe ukuba iziphumo zecaffeine kunye nokukhanya kukuziphatha okuchaphazela ukungalali kakuhle kunye nokubaluleka kokulala kakuhle ngexesha.
Kwelinye icandelo, abathathi-nxaxheba baxelelwa ukuba ukungalali ixesha elide kunokubangela ukuba umntu abe sesichengeni sokuhlaselwa sisifo sentliziyo, isifo somzimba, ukudandatheka nomhlaza.
Iimephu zeyunivesithi, ezinemifanekiso enemifanekiso, zikhuthaza abafundi ukuba bacinge ngezinto abazenzayo.
'Siyazi ukuba ayizukutshintsha indlela abafundi abaziphatha ngayo.
UProfesa Czeisler uthi: Kodwa sikholelwa ukuba banelungelo lokwazi; kanye njengokuba unelungelo lokwazi ngemiphumo yezempilo yokukhetha ukutshaya.'
Kukho inkcubeko yokuzimisela ngokufunda 'ebusuku', wongeza wathi itekhnoloji inyanzelisa abafundi ukuba balale ngokwaneleyo, nto leyo ethetha ukuba ukungalali kakuhle kuyingxaki ekhulayo.
Ukuqinisekisa ukuba ulala ngokwaneleyo, kufuneka kube 'sisikhali' sabafundi sokulwa noxinzelelo, ukudinwa noxinzelelo; kwaye ukhusele umzimba, kuba ukungalali ngokwaneleyo kubeka ingqondo kwindlela yokulamba, iyenza ihlale ilambile.
URaymond So, umfundi waseCalifornia oneminyaka eli-19 ubudala we-biology, wanceda uProfesa Czeisler ukucwangcisa isifundo, kuba wayefunde izifundo zakhe kunyaka ophelileyo kunyaka wakhe wokuqala eHarvard.
Wathi esi sifundo samvula amehlo aza afuna ukufundiswa kuyo yonke iyunivesithi.
Ukholelwa ukuba inyathelo elilandelayo kukufuna abafundi abaphumelele kwiiyunivesithi ukuba bagqibezele iinkqubo ezithile ngaphambi kokuba bangene kwiinkampani ezifuna umsebenzi.
UProfesa Czeisler ucebisa ukuba abafundi bacinge ngokufaka ii-alamu zokulumkisa xa belele naxa bevuka, eziquka ukukhanya okuluhlaza kwe-LED, ezinokubangela ukuba umntu aphazamiseke xa elele, nto leyo enokubangela iingxaki zokulala.
