I-HIV/AIDS: I-China inika ingxelo yokunyuka kwe-14% kwintsholongwane entsha
I-China inike ingxelo yokunyuka kwe-14% kwinani labantu abanentsholongwane kaGawulayo kunye ne-HIV.
Ngaphezulu kwe-820,000 yamatyala kweli lizwe ngokwemibiko yabasemagunyeni bezempilo.
Phantse bangama-40 000 abantu abatsha abafunyaniswe benesi sifo kwikota yesibini yonyaka ka-2018 kuphela.
Inani elikhulu labantu abatsha abanesi sifo lisuka kulwalamano olungaqhelekanga, ngokungafaniyo nexesha elidlulileyo.
Ngokwesiqhelo, intsholongwane kaGawulayo isasazeka ngokukhawuleza kwiindawo ezithile zase China ngenxa yokunikela ngegazi elosulelekileyo.
Kodwa inani labantu abanentsholongwane ye-HIV kule ndlela liye lehla laya kutsho kwi-zero, amagosa ezempilo ase China axela kwintlanganiso kwiPhondo lase Yunnan.
Nangona kunjalo, inani labantu abane-HIV kunye ne-AIDS e-China linyuka ngama-100 000 ngonyaka.
Ukosuleleka nge-HIV ngesondo yingxaki enkulu kubantu abathandana besini esinye e-China.
Ubufanasini buye bapheliswa ngokusemthethweni e-China ngowe-1997, kodwa ucalucalulo kubantu abathandana besini esahlukileyo luyanda.
Ngenxa yokuba eli lizwe lihlala liphila ngemithetho yakudala, uphando luye lwaqikelela ukuba ama-70 ukuya kuma-90 ekhulwini amadoda awela kwisondo namanye amadoda ekugqibeleni atshata namabhinqa.
Uninzi lwezifo ezosulelayo zibangelwa kukulala ngesondo ngaphandle kokukhusela umtshato.
Ukususela ngo-2003, urhulumente waseTshayina uye waqinisekisa ukuba amayeza e-HIV ayafumaneka ngokubanzi njengenxalenye yokulwa nale ngxaki.
