Amagama abo bonke abamangali abaxhasa uGrace v. Sessions athi isimangalo se-American Civil Liberties Unionfiled esenziwe ngo-Agasti malunga neenkqubo zikarhulumente asizange saziwe.
Uthe intombi yakhe "kunye noonyana bakhe ababini ababandakanyekayo" bamxhaphaza kodwa abasemagunyeni baseMelika basichitha isicelo sakhe sokukhuselwa ngoJulayi 20.
Wavalelwa eTexas.
Amagqwetha kaRhulumente axhasa uGrace achaze iEl Salvador, iHonduras neGuatemala, ezivelisa inani elikhulu labantu abafuna ukukhuselwa eMelika, njengelizwe elinengxaki enkulu yezigebenga kunye nobundlobongela basekhaya.
Imithetho emitsha yase-US malunga nabafuna ukukhoselwa iguqula isigqibo se-Immigration Appeals Board sika-2014 esenza ukuba abafudukayo abangenazo iimpepha ezisemthethweni babaleke ubundlobongela basekhaya kwaye bafune ukukhoselwa.
U-Mongameli we-District of Columbia, uKarl Racine, kwintetho yakhe yangoLwesihlanu, wathi le mithetho mitsha "iyaziphosa imithetho yeminyaka emininzi yelizwe, yesizwe neyamazwe aphesheya".
"Umthetho welizwe ufuna ukuba zonke izicelo zokukhuselwa ziqwalaselwe ngokusekwe kulwazi olukhethekileyo kwaye ukuba isicelo senziwe kwaye le mithetho intsha imiselweyo iyagqitha kulo", kubhaliwe kwisishwankathelo esifakwe ngabahlobo benkundla.
Iijaji zithi kwincwadana emfutshane ukuba izithintelo zokufudukela kwelinye ilizwe ziyingozi kuqoqosho lwaseMelika, zisithi zinokubangela ukuba abantu babe ngabarhwebi kwaye "banike imisebenzi ebalulekileyo".
NgoJuni, iJaji eyiNtloko, uJeff Sessions, wacela ukuba iijaji ezijongene nokufudukela kwelinye ilizwe zingabi sabapha indawo yokuhlala abantu abaxhatshazwayo ngenxa yobundlobongela basekhaya kunye nobundlobongela beqela.
Kwisaziso sikaSessions sangoJuni 11 malunga nezi ndlela, wathi: "Indawo yokhuseleko inikwa abo bashiya ilizwe labo lokuzalwa ngenxa yokuxhatshazwa okanye uloyiko olubanzi lokucalulwa ngenxa yohlanga, inkolo, ubuzwe, ubume beqela okanye iimbono zabo zopolitiko".
Iindawo zokukhusela azenzelwanga ukunciphisa ubunzima benkxalabo; nokuba yeyiphi na ingxaki enkulu abantu abajongana nayo yonke imihla kwihlabathi liphela.
Umsebenzi omkhulu wokunceda ePalu ngelixa inani labantu ababuleweyo liphindwe kabini kukhangelo olukhawulezileyo lwabantu abaleleyo
Kwabasindileyo, iingxaki zazisiba nkulu njengoko ixesha lalihamba.
"Ndiziva ndinzima kakhulu", utshilo umama uRisa Kusuma, 35, owayekhusela unyana wakhe obetha umlilo kwindawo yokugcina abantu abahluphekileyo.
"Njalo ngemizuzu kuza abantu bezokunceda, beqokelela izidumbu.
Amanzi acocekileyo anqabile".
Abahlali abafumanekayo babebuyela kumakhaya abo adlakazekileyo, bathabathe izinto zabo ezikhukulisiweyo, baze bazame ukufumana izinto abaza kuzisebenzisa.
Amakhulu abantu abonzakele kwaye izibhedlele zonakaliswe yinyikima enkulu eyi-7.5.
Abanye babonzakele, kubandakanya uDwi Haris, owaphuka umqolo kunye nehlombe, elele ngaphandle kwesibhedlele somkhosi ePalu, apho izigulana zazinyangwa ngaphandle ngenxa yeenyikima ezincinci eziqhubekayo.
Iinyembezi zazehlela emehlweni akhe njengoko wayebalisa ngenyikima eyanyikima igumbi lakhe ehotele kumgangatho wesihlanu apho wayehlala khona nomfazi nonyana wakhe.
"Sasiphelelwe lixesha lokubaleka.
Ndiyayithanda le ndonga, ndicinga njalo", utshilo uHaris kwi-Associated Press, esongeza ukuba usapho lwakhe lwalusezidolophini ukuya emtshatweni.
"Ndandimva umfazi wam ekhala efuna uncedo, kodwa emva koko wathi cwaka.
Andazi ukuba kwenzeke ntoni kuye nakunyana wam.
Ndiyathemba ukuba bakhuselekile".
U-ambassador wase-US utyhola i-China 'ngokuvimba' ngeentengiso zayo 'ze-censorship'
Emva kweveki enye iphephandaba laseTshayina liphumeze isibhengezo esinemaphepha amane kwiphephandaba laseMelika elizibiza ngokuba liyakunceda urhwebo lwe-US ne-China, ummeli wase-US e-China utyhola urhulumente wase-Beijing ngokusebenzisa iphephandaba lase-US ukukhuthaza ulawulo lwakhe.
NgoLwesithathu, uMongameli wase-US uDonald Trump wabhengeza ukuba iChina Daily ihlawule imali eninzi kwiDes Moines Register, iphephandaba elithengiswa kakhulu e-Iowa, emva kokumangalela i-China ngokuzama ukuphazamisa unyulo lwe-US ngo-Novemba 6, i-China iyayikhaba yonke loo nto.
UTrump utyhola iBeijing ngokuzama ukuphazamisa unyulo lwaseMelika, nto leyo abasemagunyeni baseMelika abayithetha kwiReuters njengenyathelo elitsha kwisicwangciso esitsha esenziwe nguWashington sokubeka uxinzelelo e-China.
Ngelixa kuyinto eqhelekileyo ukuba oorhulumente bamanye amazwe basebenzise izibhengezo zorhwebo ukukhuthaza ishishini, iBeijing neWashington ngoku zixakekile kwimfazwe yorhwebo eye yathatha inqanaba elitsha ukuya kuthi ga ekunyuseni irhafu kwiimveliso ezithunyelwa kwelinye ilizwe.
I-China iphinde yaziphindezela kwirhafu emva kokuba imfazwe yorhwebo iqale apho yayicwangciselwe ukuhlasela abathumeli ngaphandle base-Iowa abaxhasa iPhathi kaTrump yeRiphabhlikhi, ngokutsho kweengcali zobudlelwane be-US-China.
UTery Branstad, ummeli wase-US e-China nomlawuli wexesha elide wase-Iowa, umthengisi omkhulu weemveliso zolimo e-China, wathi urhulumente wase-Beijing uyingozi kumafama, abalimi kunye namashishini aseMelika.
I-China, uBranstad wabhala kwingxelo ye-Des Moines Register ngeCawa, "Ngoku sele iqinisile ekuyekiseni nasekuhambiseni iintengiso ezichasene nokuziphatha kumaphephandaba ethu azimeleyo".
"Ukuze isasaze ulawulo lwayo, urhulumente wase China usebenzisa inkcubeko yaseMelika yenkululeko yokuthetha kunye nenkululeko yeendaba ngokubeka iintengiso ezihlawulwayo kwiDes Moines Register", utshilo uBranstad.
"Ngokwahlukileyo, kwizitolo zeendaba ezisezitratweni apha eBeijing, ufumana iingxelo ezivela kubantu abangonwabanga ngurhulumente kodwa awufumani umfanekiso wokwenene weengcamango ezahlukeneyo zokuba amaTshayina anokuba kwicala elibi loqoqosho, kuba amajelo eendaba aphethwe yiQela elilawulayo leQela lamaKomanisi laseTshayina", ubhale watsho.
Wongeze wathi "enye yeephephandaba ezinkulu e-China iye yaphepha ukubhengeza" ibali lakhe, nangona engazange alichaze igama laloo phephandaba.
Abahlalutyi babelumkise ukuba amaRephabliki aya kushiya abafazi abavota kanye ngaphambi konyulo lwasembindini kunye noKavanaugh Debacle
Ngelixa uninzi lwabantu abaphezulu kwiqela leRepublican belilindele kwaye belizakuxhasa umviwa weNkundla ePhakamileyo, uBrett Kavanaugh, obekwa ityala lokuxhatshazwa ngokwesondo, umhlalutyi walumkisa ukuba izinto abazenzayo azizukufunyanwa kakuhle; ngakumbi, ngabafazi, ngexesha lonyulo lwasembindini.
Iimvakalelo malunga nalo mbandela zininzi kwaye uninzi lwabemi beRiphabhlikhi sele luvakalisile ukuba bafuna unyulo luqhubeke.
Ezi zinto azinakuguqulwa", utshilo uGrant Reeher, umhleli wezifundo zezopolitiko kwiSikolo seMaxwell kwiYunivesithi yaseSyracuse kwiThe Hill kwibali elipapashwe ngoMgqibelo.
UReeher wathi uyazikrokrela ukuba ingxelo yomzuzu wokugqibela kaSenator Jeff Flake (uMlawuli wase-Arizona ongumRephabliki) yokuba i-FBI iphando iya kwanela ukuvala umsindo wabavoti abanomsindo.
"Abasetyhini abasayi kuze bayilibale into eyenzeke izolo; abayi kulibala ingomso kwaye abayi kulibala ngoNovemba", utshilo uKarine Jean-Pierre, umcebisi omkhulu kunye nesithethi sesizwe seqela lophuhliso iMoveOn ngoLwesihlanu, ngokutsho kweWashington, D.C.
Ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu, abaqhankqalazi babethetha besithi "NgoNovemba!" njengoko babeqhankqalaza kwibhunga leSenate njengoko amaRephabliki alawula iKomiti yezoBulungisa akhetha ukuqhubeka nokuqinisekisa ukuqeshwa kukaKavanaugh nangona bekukho ukubhengezwa kukaGqirha Christine Blasey Ford, ngokutsho kweMic.
"Iqela leDemokhrasi lijolise kakhulu", utshilo uStu Rothenberg, umhlalutyi wezopolitiko ongenalo iqela.
"Abantu bathi, 'Kodwa ke, oku kuyinto ephakamileyo, kwaye kuyinyaniso.
Kodwa inokuba phezulu kakhulu; ngakumbi phakathi kwabafazi abangaqinisekanga ukuba baza kuvota phi emaphandleni kunye nabavoti abancinci, abaneminyaka eli-18 ukuya kwengama-29 ubudala, ukuba abathandi umongameli, abafane bavote".
Nangona uFord wayechaza ngokucacileyo ngaphambi kokuba anike ubungqina esidlangalaleni malunga nokuchazwa kwakhe ngokwesini ngumgqatswa weNkundla ePhakamileyo, abagxeki bathi izinto azinakwamkelwa kakuhle ukuba amaRephabliki ayaqhubeka nokuqinisekisa.
"Le nto yenze isiphithiphithi kwiqela leRepublican Party", utshilo uMichael Steele, owayesakuba ngumphathi weKomiti yeSizwe yeRiphabhlikhi, kwingxelo ye-NBC News ekuqaleni kweveki ephelileyo.
"Ayikuko ukhetho lwekomiti okanye ukhetho olungagqibekanga okanye ukuba uKavanaugh uya kuhlala phantsi, kodwa malunga nendlela amaRephabliki aziphatha ngayo kule meko kwaye amncedise", utshilo uGuy Cecil, umphathi we-Priorities USA, iqela elixhasa ukhetho lwamaDemocrats, kwingxelo yeendaba.
Nangona kunjalo, abantu baseMelika babonakala behlukene phakathi malunga nokuba ngubani abanokumthemba emva kobungqina bukaFord noKavanaugh, uninzi luthanda ubungqina bokugqibela.
Uphando olutsha olwenziwe yi-YouGov lubonisa ukuba iipesenti ezingama-41 zabaphenduli bakholelwa ngokuqinisekileyo okanye banokuyithemba ubungqina bukaFord, ngelixa iipesenti ezingama-35 zithi bayakholelwa ngokuqinisekileyo okanye banokuyithemba ubungqina bukaKavanaugh.
Ngokwahlukileyo, ama-38 ekhulwini athi acinga ukuba uKavanaugh usenokuba okanye ngokuqinisekileyo wayexoka xa wayenikela ubungqina, ngoxa ama-30 ekhulwini athi kunjalo ngoFord.
Emva kwesicelo sikaFlake, i-FBI ngoku iphenya ngezityholo ezenziwe nguFord kunye nomtshutshisi onguDeborah Ramirez, ngokutsho kweThe Guardian.
UFord wangqina phambi kweKomiti yezoBulungisa yeSenate phantsi kwesifungo kwiveki ephelileyo esithi uKavanaugh wayesele enxilile kwaye wamxhaphaza xa wayeneminyaka eli-17.
