Umqambi weWebhu uceba ukuqala i-intanethi entsha ukuze akhuphisane neGoogle neFacebook
UTim Berners-Lee, umqambi weWebhu yeHlabathi, uza kuseka inkampani eza kukhuphisana neFacebook, Amazon neGoogle.
Iprojekthi yakutshanje ye-tech giant, i-Inrupt, yinkampani esekwe kwi-Berners-Lee's Solid.
I-Solid ivumela abasebenzisi ukuba bakhethe ukuba idatha yabo igcinwa phi kwaye ngubani onokuthi ayifumane.
Kudliwano-ndlebe olukhethekileyo neFast Company, uBerners-Lee wahlekisa esithi injongo ye-Inrupt "kukulawula umhlaba".
"Kufuneka siyenze ngoku", utsho ngale nkampani aza kuyivula.
"Ngumzuzu wembali".
Inkqubo isebenzisa itekhnoloji yeSolid ukuvumela abantu ukuba bafake "i-database yabucala kwi-intanethi" okanye i-POD.
Inokufaka uluhlu lweekhompyutha, uluhlu lwezinto ekufuneka zenziwe, ikhalenda, ithala leencwadi zomculo kunye nezinye izixhobo zobuqu nezomsebenzi.
Ifana neGoogle Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, iSlack neSpotify zonke zifumaneka kwisikhangeli esinye ngexesha elinye.
Into eyenza i-website ibe yeyona ikhethekileyo kukuba ivumela umsebenzisi ukuba afumane ulwazi oluthile.
Inkampani ibiza oku "ngokuxhobisa abantu ngemininingwane".
Ingcamango ye-Inrupt, ngokwe-CEO uJohn Bruce, kukuba inkampani kufuneka izise ubuchule, iinkqubo kunye nobuchule obufanelekileyo ukunceda ukwenza i-Solid ifikeleleke kubo bonke.
Okwangoku, inkampani yeBerners-Lee, uBruce, i-web security software evela kwi-IBM, abanye abaphuhlisi beprogram banikwe iikhontrakthi zokusebenza kwiiprojekthi ezahlukeneyo kunye ne-ejensi yokuzithandela yokubhala ikhowudi.
Ukuqala kule veki, abaphuhlisi behlabathi banokufaka ii-software ze-Inrupt kwi-intanethi besebenzisa izixhobo ezikhoyo kwiwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
UBerners-Lee wathi yena neqela lakhe bebengathethi ne "Facebook neGoogle malunga nokuba bangayiqala na utshintsho apho indlela yabo yokusebenza inokupheliswa ngokukhawuleza.
"Asizukucela enye".
Kwinkcazo yeMedium epapashwe ngoMgqibelo, uBerners-Lee wabhala ukuba i-Inrupt "ijolise ekunikezeleni amandla oshishino kunye neenkqubo zokunceda ukukhusela ukuthembeka kunye nokuthembeka kwewebhusayithi entsha eyakhiwe kusetyenziswa iSolide".
Ngowe-1994, uBerners-Lee waguqula i-Intanethi xa waseka i-International Web Forum kwi-Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
Kwiinyanga ezimbalwa ezidlulileyo, uBerners-Lee uye waba lilizwi eliguqukayo kwiingxoxo ezijolise ekuqinisekiseni ukuba i-Intanethi ayinakugwetywa.
Nangona esungula i-Inrupt, uBerners-Lee uya kuhlala engumSeki kunye ne-CEO ye-International Web Forum, iWeb Foundation kunye ne-Open Data Institute.
"Ndiqinisekile ngekamva lehlabathi", utshilo uBerners-Lee.
UBernard Vann: Umamkeli we-WW1 Victoria Cross owenziwe ngomsitho
Umfundisi weCawa yaseNgilani owafumana iVictoria Cross kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi I njengomphumi-mkhosi wenziwa umnyhadala kwisixeko sakhe emva kweminyaka eli-100.
ULieutenant Colonel Revera Bernard Vann wanikwa le ndondo nge-29 Septemba 1918 kwiMfazwe yaseBellenglise naseLehaucourt.
Nangona kunjalo, wabulawa ngumgxeki emva kweentsuku ezine kwaye akazange azi ukuba uphumelele eyona nto ibalaseleyo kumkhosi waseBritane.
NgoMgqibelo, ilitye lesikhumbuzo lakhe lamiselwa ngabazukulwana bakhe ababini kumngcwabo waseRushden, eNorthamptonshire.
Omnye wabazukulwana bakhe, uMichael Vann, wathi "ngumqondiso omangalisayo" ukuba ilitye libekwe ngokufanelekileyo kwiminyaka eli-100 emva kwedabi elabangela ukuba utatomkhulu wakhe afumane imbasa yakhe yokuqala.
NgokweLondon Gazette, nge-29 Septemba 1918; uLieutenant Colonel Vann wakhokela iqela lakhe elidlula kwi-St-Quentin Tunnel "kwilifu elimnyama nelichithwa ziimbumbulu ezininzi zomhlaba kunye nezikhali".
Emva koko wakhawuleza waya kwindawo ekwakugqalwa kuyo umlo waza "ngobugorha obukhulu" wakhokela umkhosi wakhe ukuba uqhubeke nokugqogqa umkhosi weentshaba de yena ngokwakhe wakwazi ukubetha amaqela amathathu omkhosi.
U-Lieutenant Colonel wabulawa ngumgcini-mkhosi waseJamani ngo-Oktobha 4, 1918, kwinyanga enye ngaphambi kokuphela kwemfazwe.
UMichael Vann, oneminyaka engama-72 ubudala, wathi umsebenzi katatomkhulu "yayinto endingazange ndiyenze kuba yayimenza athobeke".
Yena nomntakwabo, uGqr James Vann, babeka iintyatyambo engcwabeni emva komngcwabo, owawukhokelwa yiBrentwood Imperial Youth Band.
"Ndiziva ndinelunda kakhulu ngokuba yinxalenye yale mbutho", utshilo uMichael Vann, "kwaye wongeza wathi "amandla eqhawe lokwenene abonakaliswa kukuncedwa ngabantu abaninzi".
Abaxhasi be-MMA bahlala ubusuku bonke belinde umdlalo we-Bellator 206, kodwa babukela i-movie ye-movie ebizwa ngokuba yiPeppa Pig.
Khawufane ucinge, uchithe ubusuku bonke ubukele umdlalo weqakamba weBellator 206 kwaye waphoswa kukubukela umlo owawulindelwe kakhulu.
Ishedyuli yaseSan Jose yayineembambano ezili-13, kubandakanya ezithandathu ezilindeleke kakhulu kwaye ziboniswa kwangoko ebusuku e-UK kwiSiteshi 5.
Ngentsimbi yesithandathu kusasa, xa uGegard Mousasi noRory MacDonald babelungiselela ukudibana, ababukeli beTV base-UK bathe manga xa isilwanyana esibukeleyo saba sisilwanyana esaziwa ngokuba yiPeppa Pig.
Abanye abazange bayithande into eyenzekayo emva kokuba bechithe ubusuku bonke bebukele imfazwe.
Omnye umlandeli kuTwitter wachaza ukuguqulwa kweentente zabantwana "njengokuhlekisa okungekho ngqiqweni".
"Ngumthetho welizwe ukuba i-6: 00 AM yayingafanelekanga xa bayitshintsha baba neenkqubo zabantwana", utshilo uDave Schwartz, usekela mongameli we-Bellator wezentengiso kunye nonxibelelwano, xa ebuzwa malunga nemiboniso.
""Peppa the pig", ewe".
UMongameli we-Bellator, uScott Coker, uthe baya kwenza utshintsho kwisicwangciso sabo kubandakanya ababukeli beTV base-UK kwiintsuku ezizayo.
"Ndicinga ukuba xa ndicinga ngokujonga umlo ugqityiwe, ndicinga ukuba mhlawumbi banokwenza okuthile ngawo", utshilo uCoker.
"Kodwa ngentsimbi yesithandathu ngentsasa yangeCawa xa ndihamba kwaye asinakwenza nto ngayo de ibe yiCawa ngexesha lethu, kwaye ngoMvulo ngexesha labo.
Kodwa siza kwenza okuthile.
Ndithembe, xa nditshintsha iincwadi, kwakukho iincwadi ezininzi ezazibuya kwaye zonke zazingenazo iindaba ezilungileyo.
Besizama ukuyilungisa le ngxaki, sicinga ukuba yingxaki yobuchwepheshe.
Kodwa yayingeyonyani leyo, yayingumbandela karhulumente.
Ndiyathembisa ukuba kwixesha elizayo akuyi kuphinda kwenzeke.
Siza kuyidibanisa ibe yimilo emihlanu endaweni yemithandathu; njengoko besisoloko sisenza kwaye sizama ukunika abalandeli bethu okuninzi kwaye siphumelele.
Yinto ebuhlungu le yenzekileyo".
Inkqubo yerediyo iDesert Island Discs: UTom Daley uziva 'ethobekile' ngesondo
Umxumi weOlimpiki uTom Daley uthi wakhula eziva ehlazekile ngenxa yesini sakhe, kodwa oko kwamenza waziva enelunda.
Lo mdlali oneminyaka engama-24 ubudala uthi akazange ayiqonde de waya kwisikolo samabanga aphakamileyo apho wafumanisa ukuba "akukho mntu unjengam".
Xa wayeqala ukubonakala kwiDesert Island Discs yeRadio 4, uLauren Laverne wathi uthethe ngamalungelo abantu abangamafanasini ukuze anike abanye "ithemba".
Kwakhona uthi ukuba ngumama kuye kwabangela ukuba angabi namdla wokuwina imbasa kwiiOlimpiki.
Umnxibelelanisi wexesha elide, uKirsty Young, wayethathe iinyanga ezininzi ekhefu ngenxa yempilo.
Ukubonakala njengomsulwa kumdlalo wokuqala kaLaverne, uDaley wathi uziva "phantsi" komnye umntu oselula kuba "kwakungavumelekanga kusapho ukuba athande amakhwenkwe namantombazana".
Uthi: "Kude kube namhlanje, ukuziva ndingento yanto nokungafani nam kuye kwaba yeyona nto inamandla kum, yandomeleza".
Wayefuna ukubonisa ukuba "unguthile", watsho ukuze angadumazi nabani na xa efumanisa ngesini sakhe.
Umdlali weOlimpiki ophumelele imbasa kabini uye waba ngumkhuseli wesini esifanayo owaziwayo kwaye wasebenzisa ukuthatha inxaxheba kwakhe kwiiNgingqi ezithetha isiNgesi kunye neBritish Colonial Commonwealth Games e-Australia ukucela amazwe amaninzi ukuba ayeke ukwenza izenzo zesini esifanayo zibe sisono.
Uthe wayeka kuba wayeziva enethuba lokuphila ubomi bakhe ngokukhululekileyo kwaye efuna ukunika abanye "ithemba".
Umdlali webhola ophumelele iimbasa ezintathu zehlabathi uthe ukuthandana nomvelisi wefilimu waseMelika, uDustin Lance Black, abadibana naye ngo-2013; "yamothusa".
UDaley watshata nomntu ophumelele i-Oscar, omdala kunaye ngeminyaka engama-20, kunyaka ophelileyo kodwa uthi umahluko weminyaka awuzange ube yingxaki.
"Ufumana izinto ezininzi xa usemncinci"; uthi xa wayeneminyaka eli-14 ubudala, waya kwiiOlimpiki zakhe zokuqala kwaye utata wakhe wafa ngumhlaza kwiintsuku ezintathu kamva, wathi kunzima ukufumana umntu oneminyaka efanayo naye.
Aba bahlobo baba ngabazali ngoJuni, bazala unyana ogama linguRobert Ray Black-Daley, kwaye uDaley wathi "zonke iingcinga zakhe" zatshintsha.
"Ukuba ububuze ukuba yintoni eyona nto ndiyifunayo kulo nyaka uphelileyo, bendingathi, 'Ndifuna ukuphumelela imbasa yegolide.'"
"Uyazi, kukho izinto ezibaluleke ngakumbi kunemali yegolide kwiiOlimpiki.
