Iinqanawa ezintsha zaseJamani zavunyelwa ukuba ziqalise ukusebenza ngo-2014 ukuze zithathe indawo yeenqanawa ezindala zeMfazwe ebandayo, kodwa bezingazukufumaneka kude kube ngunyaka olandelayo ngenxa yenkqubo engalunganga kunye neendleko eziphezulu, ngokutsho kweendaba zalapha.
Ukuvunyelwa kolwandle kwi-Rheinland-Pfalz, inqanawa ekhokelayo kwi-Baden-Wuerttemberg brand brand brand, iye yamiselwa kude kube lixesha lokuqala lonyaka ka-2019, ngokutsho kwe-Die Zeit, ecaphula isithethi somkhosi.
I-Shipyards yafumana ezinye iinqanawa zokulwa ngo-2014, kodwa iingxaki zokuhambisa zabangela ukuba le projekthi enkulu ibe semngciphekweni.
I-Baden-Wuerttemberg-class i-battleship, iinqanawa ezine ezi-Battleship, zi-battleship ezi-odolwa ngumkhosi waselwandle ngo-2007 njengendawo yokutshintsha iinqanawa ezindala zaseBremen.
Ngokuqinisekileyo kufuneka ibe nezixhobo ezinamandla, iintlobo ezahlukeneyo zeemitha zokukhusela i-aircraft kunye ne-ship missiles kunye nobuchwepheshe bokungena emanzini omchasi, njengokunciphisa umbono we-radar, imiqondiso ye-IRD kunye nokuva kunye ne-audio.
Enye into ebalulekileyo kwezi nqanawa kukuhlala ixesha elide, kwaye kufuneka kubekho ithuba lokuba iinqanawa ezintsha zifakwe elwandle ubuncinci iminyaka emibini ukusuka kwindawo engaphandle kwelizwe elivela kulo.
Nangona kunjalo, ukulibaziseka okuqhubekayo kuthetha ukuba iinqanawa zinobuchwephesha obuphambili, njengoko bekuxelwe kwangaphambili ukuba bunokwenza iJamani ibe namandla okuhamba, obuya kuba budala xa busetyenziswa, ngokutsho kweZeit.
Le F125 yafumana ingxubusho kumajelo eendaba kunyaka ophelileyo xa i-Air Force yasikhaba esidlangalaleni isivumelwano sokukhwela inqanawa yaza yayibuyisela kwi-Blohm & Voss shipyard eHamburg.
Yayikokokuqala ukuba inqanawa yomkhosi weemfazwe ibuyiselwe kumenzi wayo emva kokuba ishiywe.
Akukho sizathu sicacileyo sokuba ibuyiselwe, kodwa amaphephandaba aseJamani athi kukho iziphene ezininzi "kwiinkqubo nakwimishini" ezenza ukuba inqanawa ingabi nexesha elide ukuya emfazweni.
Ngokukodwa, iziphene zenkqubo zazinzima kakhulu xa iinqanawa zeBaden-Wuerttemberg zazisebenza kunye neqela labakhweli abali-120, inxalenye yabasebenzi ababesebenzisa iinqanawa ezindala zaseBremen.
Kwakhona, kwafunyaniswa ukuba inqanawa inobunzima obukhulu obuya kunciphisa ukusebenza kwayo kwaye kunciphise amandla omkhosi waselwandle ngokufumana izinto ezongezelelweyo kwiinqanawa ezihlaziyiweyo kwixesha elizayo.
I-Rheinland-Pfalz, enobunzima obuziitoni ezingama-7 000, ibonakala iphindwe kabini kunenqanawa efanayo neyasetyenziswa yiJamani kwiMfazwe yesibini yeHlabathi.
Ukongeza kwiimveliso ezinesiphene, iindleko zeprojekthi yonke, kubandakanya noqeqesho lwabakhweli, ziya kuba yingxaki.
Kubikwa ukuba iye yafikelela kwi-euro eziibhiliyoni ezi-3.1 (i-US $ 3.6 billion), ukusuka kwi-euro eziibhiliyoni ezi-2.2 ezacetywayo.
Iingxaki ezijongene nezi ntlobo zintsha zeenqanawa ziyaqhubeka ukuvela kwakhona ngexesha apho kwakusandula ukuvela iingxelo zokuba amandla omkhosi waselwandle waseJamani ayanyamalala.
Ekuqaleni konyaka, uHans-Peter Bartels, oyintloko yeKomiti yoKhuselo yePalamente yaseJamani, wavuma ukuba ngoku uMkhosi weLwandle "ufuna iinqanawa ezinokukhusela".
Lo mphathi wathi ingxaki iye yanda njengoko iminyaka ihamba, njengoko iinqanawa ezindala ziye zaphela kodwa azikhange zenziwe ezinye.
Wazikhalela esithi akukho nqanawa yaseBaden-Wuerttemberg eye yafumana imvume yokungena emkhosini.
