Inyikima neTsunami eIndonesia
Ubuncinci abantu abangama-384 babulawa yinyikima enkulu kunye netsunami eyahlasela isixeko saseIndonesia iPalu ngoLwesihlanu, ngokutsho kwabasemagunyeni, ngelixa inani labantu abafayo kulindeleke ukuba lenyuke.
Ngelixa iinkqubo zokufumana kunye nokuthumela zingasebenzi, amagosa oncedo awazange akwazi ukufumana ingxelo evela eDonggala, emantla ePalu kufutshane nendawo eyanyikima ngayo inyikima enkulu eyi-7.5.
EPalu, abantu abangaphezu kwe-16 000 baye basindiswa emva kokuba intlekele yenzeke.
Nazi ezinye zeenkcukacha ezibalulekileyo ngePalu neDonggala, kwisiqithi saseSulawesi:
IPalu yidolophu ekwiPhondo laseMntla Sulawesi, kufutshane nonxweme olusentshona lweSulawesi, ene-estimated population of 379,800 in 2017.
Esi sixeko sasiza kukhumbula iminyaka engama-40 eyadlulayo xa sasithwaxwa yinyikima enkulu kunye netsunami.
I-Donggala yindawo engaphaya kweekhilomitha ezingama-300 (i-180 miles) ubude, kufutshane nonxweme olusemantla ntshona esiqithi saseSulawesi.
Le ndawo, yindawo yolawulo ephantsi kwephondo, inabantu abaqikelelwa kuma-299,200 ngo-2017.
Ukurhweba ngeentlanzi kunye nemfuyo zezona zinto ziphambili kuqoqosho kwiPhondo laseMntla Sulawesi, ngakumbi, kunxweme lwaseDonggala.
Imigodi ye-nickel nayo ibalulekile kweli phondo, kodwa eyona ndawo iphambili kwimigodi eMorowali, kwelinye icala lonxweme lwaseSulawesi.
IPalu neDonggala ziye zathwaxwa ziitsunami eziliqela kule minyaka iyi-100 idlulileyo, ngokutsho kwe-Indonesian Disaster Management Agency.
Ngowe-1938, itsunami yabulala abantu abangaphezu kwama-200 yaza yonakalisa amakhulu ezindlu eDonggala.
I-tsunami yahlasela i-Donggala entshona ngo-1996, yabulala abantu abasithoba.
I-Indonesia ibekwe kumda we-Pacific Ocean kwaye ixhatshazwa ziinyikima rhoqo.
Nazi ezinye zeenyikima ezinkulu kunye neetsunami ezenzeke kwiminyaka yakutshanje:
2004: Inyikima enkulu yenzeka kunxweme olusentshona lwephondo lase Aceh eIndonesia kumantla eSumatra nge-26 kaDisemba, yabangela itsunami eyachaphazela amazwe ali-14, yabulala abantu abangama-226 000 kunxweme loLwandlekazi lwaseIndiya, isiqingatha sabo singabemi base Aceh.
Ngo-2005: Kwabakho inyikima enkulu kunxweme lwaseSumatra ngasekupheleni kukaMatshi nasekuqaleni kuka-Aprili.
Amakhulu abantu afela kwisiqithi saseNias, esikunxweme lwaseSumatra.
Ngo-2006: Inyikima enkulu eyi-6.8 yahlasela isiqithi saseIndonesia, iJava, yaza yabangela itsunami eyabulala abantu abamalunga nabayi-700.
Ngo-2009: Inyikima enkulu enobungakanani be-7.6 yenzeka kufutshane nesixeko sasePadang, ikomkhulu lephondo laseNtshona Sumatra.
Kwafa abantu abangaphezu kwe-1 100.
Ngo-2010: Inyikima enkulu eyabangela itsunami kwisiqithi saseMentawai, kumntla weSumatra, yashiya amanzi enyuka kangangeemitha ezili-10 kumhlaba, atshabalalisa iidolophana ezininzi kwaza kwafa abantu abayi-300.
2016: Inyikima encinci yahlasela iPidie Jaya eAceh, yabangela umonakalo omkhulu kwaye yabangela uloyiko kubantu abaninzi kuba yayisikhumbuza ukuba akuzange kubekho itsunami eyabulala abantu abaninzi ngo-2004.
Akukho tsunami yenzekileyo ngeli xesha, kodwa abantu abangaphezu kwe-100 babulawa ngamanzi.
2018: Inyikima enkulu yahlasela isiqithi esithandwayo ngabakhenkethi saseIndonesia iLombok, yabulala abantu abangaphezu kwama-500, ubukhulu becala kumantla esiqithi.
Inyikima yonakalisa amawaka ezakhiwo yaza yashiya amawaka abakhenkethi bengenamakhaya okwethutyana.
