Ayingeloxesha lokuqala uPalin etyholwa ngezityholo zolwaphulo-mthetho.
NgoDisemba 2017, watyholwa ngokuxhaphaza uyise, uTodd Palin.
Unina, uSarah Palin, wabiza amapolisa ukuba axele ngolwaphulo-mthetho.
Ngoku uza kuxoxwa ityala lakhe kwiNkundla yaseAlaska.
NgoJanuwari 2016, wabekwa ityala lobundlobongela basekhaya, ukuphazamisa ingxelo yolwaphulo-mthetho lwasekhaya kunye nokuba semandleni xa esele utywala obunxulumene naloo nto.
Intombazana awayethandana nayo yayifuna ukuba imbethe ebusweni.
USarah Palin wacekiswa ngamaqela omkhosi wamajoni ngo-2016 emva kokudibanisa indlela enobundlobongela unyana wakhe awayeziphatha ngayo kunye noxinzelelo olwalubangelwa kukuya e-Iraq.
