"USayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov wenzakalise, wabulala, waza wabulala iintsapho kunye nabahlobo baka Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza noAlejandro Damian Pagnucco", itsho le ngxelo.
