UMlawuli weNdlu yeeNdlu uthi uNigel FARAGE kufuneka anikwe imbopheleleko yokuthetha nge-UK ukuba ihambe kwi-EU
UNigel Farage uzimisele 'ukukhuthaza abantu' namhlanje kumngcelele we-Tory Party Congress.
Owayesakuba yinkokheli ye-UKIP uthi abezopolitiko kufuneka baphume 'kwizigcawu' ezibangelwa kukugxeka i-EU, apho ilungu lePalamente eliphuma kwiqela lika-Theresa May lathi kufuneka abe ngoyena mntu uthetha ne-EU.
IParliamentary non-conservative Peter Bone uxelele abantu ababekhenketha eBirmingham ukuba iBritane 'iya kuba iphumile emtshatweni' ukuba uMnu Farage ebeyiNgqongqoshe we-UK's Withdrawal from the European Union.
Kodwa ingxaki kaMiss May yayikukudibanisa oogxa bakhe abahlukeneyo ukuze amaTory afuna ukuhlala kwi-EU aye kwimiboniso yokuchasana ne-UK ishiya i-EU ezixekweni.
Inkulumbuso inengxaki yokugcina isicwangciso sayo sokuphuma kwe-UK kwi-EU ngexesha lokuhlaselwa ngabathandi be-UK ukuba baphume kwi-EU kunye nabathandi be-EU.
Abaxhasi bakhe bathi uya kuqhubeka nokuzama ukudibana neBelgium nangona abanye bengayifuni kwaye bamnyanzela ukuba agxeke i-EU kunye ne-Labour Party ngokukhetha kwakhe.
UMnu Bone uxelele abo babekwiphulo elithi Leave Means Leave eSolihull ukuba ufuna 'ukucima isicwangciso se-UK sokuphuma kwi-EU'.
Uthe uMnu Farage kufuneka afakwe kwaye anikwe uxanduva lokuthetha neBelgium.
Bathi: 'Ukuba lo mntu ebengukumkani, besingaphuma phaya.'
UMlawuli waseWellingborough uqhube wathi: "Ndiza kuxhasa ukuba i-UK ishiye i-EU kodwa kufuneka siyeke ukucwangcisa i-UK ukuba ishiye i-EU".
Ethetha nge-EU, wathi: 'Asizange silwe iimfazwe zehlabathi ukuze sibonise ukuba sinamandla.
Sifuna ukwenza imithetho yethu kweli lizwe lethu.'
UMnu Bone wazikhaba ngawo omane iimfuno zabantu ukususela kunyulo luka-2016: 'Ingcamango yokuba abantu baseBritane batshintshe iingqondo zabo kwaye bafuna ukuhlala emtshatweni ayinyani kwaphela.'
U-Andrea Jenkyns, umongameli we-Tory ofuna i-UK ihambe kwi-EU, naye owayekuloo tyelelo, uxelele oonondaba: 'Into endifuna ukuyithetha yile: Ndunankulu, phulaphula abantu.
'Icebo lokushiya i-EU alithandeki ebantwini, abachasi abayi kulivota, alithandeki kwiqela lethu kwaye abaguquli-zimvo endisebenza nabo abahamba ezitalatweni basenza ukuba siphakanyiswe kuqala.
Yiyeke loo nto uze uqale uphulaphule.'
Kwimilayezo efanayo eya kuNksz May, wathi: "Inkulumbuso ihlala emsebenzini xa igcina izithembiso zayo".
UMnu Farage uxelele abezopolitiko abakwiphulo ukuba kufuneka bazive 'benomthunzi' ukuba siza kuphambukisa isigqibo esenziwe ngexesha lephulo lika-2016.
'Okuseleyo ngoku kukuthembela phakathi kwethu, uluntu kunye nequmrhu lezopolitiko,' utshilo.
'Baya kuzama ukuphazamisa icebo lase-UK lokuphuma kwi-EU kwaye silapha namhlanje ukuxelela ukuba 'asisoze sikubekezelele ukuba ungabeki tyala.'
Kwimfundiso yakhe kwisihlwele esivuyileyo, wathi: 'Ndifuna ukufaka umda kwiinkqubo zethu zopolitiko, ezilungele ukubetha umda kwi-UK's Brexit.
'Sikhuthaza abantu ukuba bakhusele eli lizwe elisinike impumelelo yokukhupha i-UK kwi-EU kwaye asizukuphumla de siyenze, sikhokelwa, sinelunda nge-UK.'
Okwangoku, abo bafuna iBritane ihlale ekhaya bahamba baya eBirmingham ngaphambi kokuba beme iiyure ezimbini kumbindi wedolophu.
Abaguquli bathe baphakamisa iiflegi zeTory bechasa iBritane ukuba ishiye i-EU emva kokumiliselwa kweqela kule mpelaveki.
