Wongeze wathi: 'Aba ngabantu abathi sinobuchule kwaye yonke into yaseCanada inobuchule obuphezulu, imida engenamthwalo, urhwebo oluxhaphakileyo kumda waseIreland.'
'Akunjalo konke konke.
