Iinyikima ezinkulu zakutshanje ziye zaqhubeka zikhukula le ngingqi, kwaye abantu abaninzi baye bagxothwa kwizindlu ezidilikileyo ePalu.
Kodwa nangona abanye abasebenzi bakhe babekhuselekile, u-Anthonius Gunawan Agung oneminyaka engama-21 ubudala akazange avume ukushiya umsebenzi wakhe kwinqaba eyayiza kutshixizela ngendlela engaqhelekanga ngenxa yomoya olawulwayo owawuphuma kwisixeko saseMutiara Sis Al Jufri Airport ePalu.
