Ingxelo ye-Red Noise: Ukugqithisa kuyaphela ePinellas, Manatee naseSarasota
Ingxelo entsha evela kwiKomishoni yezeMpilo yezilwanyana nezoLwandle yaseFlorida ibonisa ukwehla ngokubanzi kweentlobo ezibomvu eziqhelekileyo kwiindawo zaseTampa Bay.
Ngokwe-FWC, abadlali abafanelekileyo baya kuthethwa kwiindawo zasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte naseCollier counties; oko kuthetha ukuba kukho ukuhla kokugxila kumdlalo.
Imidlalo elungileyo yeRed Tide yongeze malunga neekhilomitha ezingama-210 kumda wesanti ukusuka kumantla ePinellas ukuya emazantsi e-Lee County.
Iindawo ezinokubonwa malunga neekhilomitha ezingama-25 ukusuka kunxweme lwe-Hillsborough County, kodwa zimbalwa iindawo ezihambelana neveki ephelileyo.
Umsindo obomvu uphinde wahlolwa kwiphondo lasePasco.
Ukuxinana okuphakathi okanye kunxweme lwe Pinellas County kwaboniswa kwiveki ephelileyo, ukuxinana okuphantsi kunye nokuphezulu kunxweme lwe Hillsborough County, ukuxinana okukhulu eManatee County, apho kubonakala ngakumbi ngaphakathi nangonxweme lwe Sarasota County, ukuxinana okuphakathi kunye nokugqitha eCharlotte County, ukuxinana ngaphakathi nase Lee County kunye nokuxinana okuphezulu eCollier County.
Iingxaki zokuphefumla zisaqhubeka ukuvela kwiphondo lasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee naseCollier.
Akukho ngxaki yokuphefumla eyaxelwa kumntla ntshona weFlorida kwiveki ephelileyo.
